@baseUrl   = http://localhost:9000
@token     = your_guest_token_here
@bookingId = your_booking_id_here
@invoiceNo = INV-your_booking_id_here

### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### GUEST — Buat Link Pembayaran
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### ─── Create Payment Link (WAITING_PAYMENT) ─────────────────────────────────

# Sukses — booking dalam status WAITING_PAYMENT, kembalikan payment_url DOKU
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings/{{bookingId}}/pay
Cookie: token={{token}}

###

# Error: booking bukan dalam status WAITING_PAYMENT (400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings/{{bookingId}}/pay
Cookie: token={{token}}

###

# Error: bukan pemilik booking (403 Forbidden)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings/{{bookingId}}/pay
Cookie: token=token_user_lain

###

# Error: booking tidak ditemukan (404 Not Found)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings/booking-tidak-ada/pay
Cookie: token={{token}}

###

# Error: tidak login (401 Unauthorized)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings/{{bookingId}}/pay


### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### DOKU — Webhook Notifikasi Pembayaran
### (Biasanya dipanggil oleh server DOKU, bukan manual)
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### ─── Notifikasi Pembayaran SUCCESS ─────────────────────────────────────────

# Signature dihitung oleh DOKU server. Contoh di bawah hanya ilustrasi —
# jalankan via DOKU sandbox dashboard atau dengan client_id & secret_key asli.
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/payment/notify
Content-Type: application/json
Client-Id: your_doku_client_id
Request-Id: test-request-id-001
Request-Timestamp: 2026-05-17T10:00:00Z
Signature: HMACSHA256=your_computed_signature_here

{
  "order": {
    "invoice_number": "{{invoiceNo}}",
    "amount": 540000
  },
  "transaction": {
    "status": "SUCCESS",
    "date": "2026-05-17T10:00:00Z",
    "original_request_id": "test-request-id-001"
  }
}

###

# Notifikasi Pembayaran FAILED
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/payment/notify
Content-Type: application/json
Client-Id: your_doku_client_id
Request-Id: test-request-id-002
Request-Timestamp: 2026-05-17T10:05:00Z
Signature: HMACSHA256=your_computed_signature_here

{
  "order": {
    "invoice_number": "{{invoiceNo}}",
    "amount": 540000
  },
  "transaction": {
    "status": "FAILED",
    "date": "2026-05-17T10:05:00Z",
    "original_request_id": "test-request-id-002"
  }
}

###

# Notifikasi Pembayaran EXPIRED
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/payment/notify
Content-Type: application/json
Client-Id: your_doku_client_id
Request-Id: test-request-id-003
Request-Timestamp: 2026-05-17T11:00:00Z
Signature: HMACSHA256=your_computed_signature_here

{
  "order": {
    "invoice_number": "{{invoiceNo}}",
    "amount": 540000
  },
  "transaction": {
    "status": "EXPIRED",
    "date": "2026-05-17T11:00:00Z",
    "original_request_id": "test-request-id-003"
  }
}

###

# Error: Signature tidak valid (401 Unauthorized)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/payment/notify
Content-Type: application/json
Client-Id: your_doku_client_id
Request-Id: test-request-id-bad
Request-Timestamp: 2026-05-17T10:00:00Z
Signature: HMACSHA256=signature_salah

{
  "order": {
    "invoice_number": "{{invoiceNo}}",
    "amount": 540000
  },
  "transaction": {
    "status": "SUCCESS",
    "date": "2026-05-17T10:00:00Z",
    "original_request_id": "test-request-id-bad"
  }
}
